  "datePublished": "2025-08-30",
  "description": " Conjecture :: The anarchism of the liberal subject derives from civic duty and is thus incommensurable with decolonization.\nProof :: unproven\nclaims ::\nGiven that liberal anarchism, that is, anarchism of the liberal subject, requires itself be functional within liberalism and thus a part of liberal worlding, it must maintain compatibility with liberalism. Given the lineage of liberal anarchism is deviation of the lineage of liberal individualism, its a priori determinations may be derived from that lineage. ",
